Here is the file structure:
<pre>
~/maindir/
          subdir/
                 file
</pre>
      
And here is how to reproduce:
<pre>           
~/> emacs -q
require 'icicles [<RET>]
M-x icy-mode [<RET>]

[C-xC-f]
+ File or directory (/): ~/
[main<TAB>]
+ File or directory (/): ~/maindir/ [Sole prefix completion]
[<TAB>]
+ File or directory (/): ~/maindir// [Sole prefix completion]  <-- unexpected append of '/'
