[new:DanielDehennin:2008-06-20 20:13 UTC+2]
Sorry for the delay,

I trace mml-attach-file under emacs -Q and see that when icicles is on, the function read-file-name return 
<pre>
#("~/test" 0 6 (auto-composed t))
</pre>

